# RealTimePlotView - Live Data Visualizer

RealTimePlotView is perfect for monitoring simulations, sensors, or API metrics in real time.

## Features
- Smooth line updates  
- Adjustable update interval  
- Simple to integrate  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/26_RealTimePlotView.git
cd 26_RealTimePlotView
python visualize.py
